#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.apply.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.apply"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:1 of
msgid "Apply a function along an axis of the DataFrame."
msgstr "沿 DataFrame 的轴应用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:3 of
msgid ""
"Objects passed to the function are Series objects whose index is either "
"the DataFrame's index (``axis=0``) or the DataFrame's columns "
"(``axis=1``). By default (``result_type=None``), the final return type is"
" inferred from the return type of the applied function. Otherwise, it "
"depends on the `result_type` argument."
msgstr ""
"传递给函数的对象是 Series 对象，其索引为 DataFrame 的索引（``axis=0``）或"
" DataFrame 的列（``axis=1``）。默认情况下（``result_type=None``），最终"
"返回类型由所应用函数的返回类型推断。否则，它取决于 `result_type` 参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:9 of
msgid "Function to apply to each column or row."
msgstr "应用于每列或每行的函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:11 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the function is applied:  * 0 or 'index': apply function"
" to each column. * 1 or 'columns': apply function to each row."
msgstr ""
"应用函数的轴：  * 0 或 'index'：将函数应用于每列。 * 1 或 'columns'：将"
"函数应用于每行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:11 of
msgid "Axis along which the function is applied:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:13 of
msgid "0 or 'index': apply function to each column."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:14 of
msgid "1 or 'columns': apply function to each row."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:16 of
msgid ""
"Determines if row or column is passed as a Series or ndarray object:  * "
"``False`` : passes each row or column as a Series to the   function. * "
"``True`` : the passed function will receive ndarray objects   instead.   "
"If you are just applying a NumPy reduction function this will   achieve "
"much better performance."
msgstr ""
"确定行或列是以 Series 还是 ndarray 对象传递：  * ``False`` ：将每行或每列"
"作为 Series 传递给函数。 * ``True`` ：传递的函数将接收 ndarray 对象。   "
"如果您只是应用 NumPy 归约函数，这将获得更好的性能。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:16 of
msgid "Determines if row or column is passed as a Series or ndarray object:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:18 of
msgid "``False`` : passes each row or column as a Series to the function."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:20 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"``True`` : the passed function will receive ndarray objects instead. If "
"you are just applying a NumPy reduction function this will achieve much "
"better performance."
msgstr ""
"确定行或列是以 Series 还是 ndarray 对象传递：  * ``False`` ：将每行或每列"
"作为 Series 传递给函数。 * ``True`` ：传递的函数将接收 ndarray 对象。   "
"如果您只是应用 NumPy 归约函数，这将获得更好的性能。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:25 of
msgid ""
"These only act when ``axis=1`` (columns):  * 'expand' : list-like results"
" will be turned into columns. * 'reduce' : returns a Series if possible "
"rather than expanding   list-like results. This is the opposite of "
"'expand'. * 'broadcast' : results will be broadcast to the original shape"
"   of the DataFrame, the original index and columns will be   retained.  "
"The default behaviour (None) depends on the return value of the applied "
"function: list-like results will be returned as a Series of those. "
"However if the apply function returns a Series these are expanded to "
"columns."
msgstr ""
"这些选项仅在 ``axis=1``（列）时生效：  * 'expand' ：类列表结果将转换为列"
"。 * 'reduce' ：尽可能返回 Series 而不是扩展类列表结果。这是 'expand' 的"
"反向操作。 * 'broadcast' ：结果将广播到 DataFrame 的原始形状，保留原始"
"索引和列。  默认行为（None）取决于所应用函数的返回值：类列表结果将作为 "
"Series 返回。但如果应用函数返回 Series，则会扩展为列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:25 of
msgid "These only act when ``axis=1`` (columns):"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:27 of
msgid "'expand' : list-like results will be turned into columns."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:28 of
msgid ""
"'reduce' : returns a Series if possible rather than expanding list-like "
"results. This is the opposite of 'expand'."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:30 of
msgid ""
"'broadcast' : results will be broadcast to the original shape of the "
"DataFrame, the original index and columns will be retained."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:34 of
msgid ""
"The default behaviour (None) depends on the return value of the applied "
"function: list-like results will be returned as a Series of those. "
"However if the apply function returns a Series these are expanded to "
"columns."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:39 of
msgid "Specify type of returned object. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回对象的类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:41 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回 DataFrames 的数据类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:43 of
msgid "Specify dtype of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回 Series 的数据类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:45 of
msgid "Specify name of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回 Series 的名称。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:47 of
msgid "Specify index of returned object. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回对象的索引。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:49 of
msgid ""
"Specify whether ``func`` is an elementwise function:  * ``False`` : The "
"function is not elementwise. MaxFrame will try   concatenating chunks in "
"rows (when ``axis=0``) or in columns   (when ``axis=1``) and then apply "
"``func`` onto the concatenated   chunk. The concatenation step can cause "
"extra latency. * ``True`` : The function is elementwise. MaxFrame will "
"apply   ``func`` to original chunks. This will not introduce extra   "
"concatenation step and reduce overhead."
msgstr ""
"指定 ``func`` 是否为逐元素函数：  * ``False`` ：函数不是逐元素的。"
"MaxFrame 将尝试按行（``axis=0``）或按列（``axis=1``）连接块，然后将 ``"
"func`` 应用于连接后的块。连接步骤可能引起额外延迟。 * ``True`` ：函数是逐"
"元素的。MaxFrame 将直接将 ``func`` 应用于原始块。这不会引入额外的连接步骤"
"，减少了开销。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:49 of
msgid "Specify whether ``func`` is an elementwise function:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:51 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"``False`` : The function is not elementwise. MaxFrame will try "
"concatenating chunks in rows (when ``axis=0``) or in columns (when "
"``axis=1``) and then apply ``func`` onto the concatenated chunk. The "
"concatenation step can cause extra latency."
msgstr ""
"指定 ``func`` 是否为逐元素函数：  * ``False`` ：函数不是逐元素的。"
"MaxFrame 将尝试按行（``axis=0``）或按列（``axis=1``）连接块，然后将 ``"
"func`` 应用于连接后的块。连接步骤可能引起额外延迟。 * ``True`` ：函数是逐"
"元素的。MaxFrame 将直接将 ``func`` 应用于原始块。这不会引入额外的连接步骤"
"，减少了开销。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:55 of
msgid ""
"``True`` : The function is elementwise. MaxFrame will apply ``func`` to "
"original chunks. This will not introduce extra concatenation step and "
"reduce overhead."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:59 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:61 of
msgid "Positional arguments to pass to `func` in addition to the array/series."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的位置参数，除了数组/序列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:64 of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments to pass as keywords arguments to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的额外关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:67 of
msgid "Result of applying ``func`` along the given axis of the DataFrame."
msgstr "沿 DataFrame 给定轴应用 ``func`` 的结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:73 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.applymap`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:74 of
msgid "For elementwise operations."
msgstr "用于逐元素操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:76 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.aggregate`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:77 of
msgid "Only perform aggregating type operations."
msgstr "仅执行聚合类型操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:79 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.transform`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:80 of
msgid "Only perform transforming type operations."
msgstr "仅执行变换类型操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:83 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:84 of
msgid ""
"When deciding output dtypes and shape of the return value, MaxFrame will "
"try applying ``func`` onto a mock DataFrame,  and the apply call may "
"fail. When this happens, you need to specify the type of apply call "
"(DataFrame or Series) in output_type."
msgstr ""
"在确定输出数据类型和返回值形状时，MaxFrame 会尝试将 ``func`` 应用到一个"
"模拟的 DataFrame 上，此时 apply 调用可能会失败。发生这种情况时，你需要在 "
"output_type 中指定 apply 调用的类型（DataFrame 或 Series）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:89 of
msgid ""
"For DataFrame output, you need to specify a list or a pandas Series as "
"``dtypes`` of output DataFrame. ``index`` of output can also be "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"对于 DataFrame 输出，你需要指定一个列表或 pandas Series 作为输出 "
"DataFrame 的 ``dtypes``。还可以指定输出的 ``index``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:92 of
msgid ""
"For Series output, you need to specify ``dtype`` and ``name`` of output "
"Series."
msgstr "对于 Series 输出，你需要指定输出 Series 的 ``dtype`` 和 ``name``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:94 of
msgid ""
"For any input with data type ``pandas.ArrowDtype(pyarrow.MapType)``, it "
"will always be converted to a Python dict. And for any output with this "
"data type, it must be returned as a Python dict as well."
msgstr ""
"对于任何数据类型为 ``pandas.ArrowDtype(pyarrow.MapType)`` 的输入，它将"
"始终被转换为 Python 字典。对于任何具有此数据类型的输出，也必须以 Python "
"字典形式返回。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:99 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:110 of
msgid "Using a reducing function on either axis"
msgstr "在任一轴上使用归约函数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:123 of
msgid ""
"Passing ``result_type='expand'`` will expand list-like results to columns"
" of a Dataframe"
msgstr "传递 ``result_type='expand'`` 会将类列表结果扩展为 DataFrame 的列"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:132 of
msgid ""
"Returning a Series inside the function is similar to passing "
"``result_type='expand'``. The resulting column names will be the Series "
"index."
msgstr ""
"在函数中返回一个 Series 与传递 ``result_type='expand'`` 类似。结果列名将"
"是 Series 的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:142 of
msgid ""
"Passing ``result_type='broadcast'`` will ensure the same shape result, "
"whether list-like or scalar is returned by the function, and broadcast it"
" along the axis. The resulting column names will be the originals."
msgstr ""
"传递 ``result_type='broadcast'`` 将确保结果保持相同形状，无论函数返回的是"
"类列表还是标量，并沿轴进行广播。结果列名将保持原始列名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:153 of
msgid "Create a dataframe with a map type."
msgstr "创建一个包含映射类型的 dataframe。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.apply.df_apply:174 of
msgid "Define a function that updates the map type with a new key-value pair."
msgstr "定义一个使用新键值对更新映射类型的函数。"

